  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="7958794">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7958794/" class="title-link">论公民</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7958794"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/31678134/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u31678134-3.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/31678134/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">King</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2016-07-01"
      class="main-meta">2016-07-01 08:37:35</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7958794_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  　　霍布斯以《利维坦》名扬古今，不过那是厚积薄发之作，而此书则是其第一部作品。 　　其实两者还是有关联的，《利维坦》论述的是国家这个庞大组织，可是国家的起源是领土和人民，而后由人民决定政权形式，组成国家。所以此书论述的公民（也可以说国民）算是对《利维坦》的铺...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
